	<plot>This volume of Hudson Best Collection brings three classic Famicom puzzle games to your GameBoy Advance:1. Nuts &amp; Milk2. Binary Land3. Princess Tomato in the Salad KingdomCheat: Press and hold the A &amp; B buttons on both controllers and press Reset. If done right, the game will change to Love Story mode.Cheat: If your score is higher than 30000 pts, press Select button after you die - you will be able to enter your name on the list of the best scores.Cheat: Start a new game and pause it with the Start Button. On Player 2's controller, hold Right and B, then press Left, A, B, and Select on Player 1's controller. Press Start and a hidden message will appear.</plot>
